<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idec0bcbee-3a70-11f1-9081-fe88c1712d53" identifier="/us/usc/t51/s70104"><num value="70104">§ 70104.</num><heading> Definition of Space Launch System</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In this chapter, the term “Space Launch System” means the Space Launch System authorized under section 302 of the National Aeronautics and Space Administration Authorization Act of 2010 (<ref href="/us/usc/t42/s18322">42 U.S.C. 18322</ref>).</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idec0bcbef-3a70-11f1-9081-fe88c1712d53">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/114/90/tI/s117/a/5">Pub. L. 114–90, title I, § 117(a)(5)</ref>, <date date="2015-11-25">Nov. 25, 2015</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/129/718">129 Stat. 718</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
